<div class="com-share" data-id="13452" data-title="《不要再发明新的电影类型了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13452/medium/13452.jpg?1439441897" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13452.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
